### Login mint david - menti a tokent (futtasd először!)
# @name loginAsDavid
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "david",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {% client.global.set("davidToken", response.body.token); %}

### David létrehoz egy projektet (jegyezd meg az id-t!)
# @name createProject
POST http://localhost:8080/projects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{davidToken}}

{
  "name": "Csapatprojekt",
  "description": "Tagokkal teszteljük"
}

> {% client.global.set("projectId", response.body.id); %}

### Második user regisztrálása (Anna)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "anna",
  "email": "anna@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login mint Anna
# @name loginAsAnna
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "anna",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {% client.global.set("annaToken", response.body.token); %}

### Tagok listázása - csak az OWNER van bent (David)
GET http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{davidToken}}

### Anna próbálja listázni - 403 (még nem tag)
GET http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{annaToken}}

### David hozzáadja Annát - 201
# @name addAnna
POST http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{davidToken}}

{
  "username": "anna"
}

> {% client.global.set("annaMemberId", response.body.id); %}

### Tagok listázása - most már David (OWNER) + Anna (MEMBER)
GET http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{davidToken}}

### Anna már listázhat - tagja a projektnek
GET http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{annaToken}}

### Anna látja a projektet a saját listájában is
GET http://localhost:8080/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{annaToken}}

### Konfliktus - David újra hozzáadná Annát - 409
POST http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{davidToken}}

{
  "username": "anna"
}

### Validáció - üres username - 400
POST http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{davidToken}}

{
  "username": ""
}

### Nem létező user - 404
POST http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{davidToken}}

{
  "username": "nemletezo_user_123"
}

### Anna próbál tagot hozzáadni - 403 (csak OWNER tehet)
POST http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{annaToken}}

{
  "username": "david"
}

### Nem létező project - 404
POST http://localhost:8080/projects/9999/members
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{davidToken}}

{
  "username": "anna"
}

### Anna próbálja kivenni magát - 403 (nem OWNER)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}/members/{{annaMemberId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{annaToken}}

### Tagok listázása + David (OWNER) member id mentése
GET http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{davidToken}}

> {%
    const owner = response.body.find(member => member.role === "OWNER");
    client.global.set("davidMemberId", owner.id);
%}

### David próbálja kivenni saját magát (OWNER-t) - 400 CANNOT_REMOVE_OWNER
DELETE http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}/members/{{davidMemberId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{davidToken}}

### David kiveszi Annát - 204
DELETE http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}/members/{{annaMemberId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{davidToken}}

### Anna már nem éri el a projektet - 403
GET http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{annaToken}}

### Nem létező member id - 404
DELETE http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}/members/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{davidToken}}

### Token nélkül - 401
GET http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}/members

### Anna (MEMBER) lekéri a projektet - 200 OK (láthatja)
GET http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{annaToken}}

### Anna (MEMBER) próbálja módosítani a projektet - 403 ACCESS_DENIED
PUT http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{annaToken}}

{
  "name": "Anna szeretné átírni",
  "description": "De nem fog menni"
}

### Anna (MEMBER) próbálja törölni a projektet - 403 ACCESS_DENIED
DELETE http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{annaToken}}

### David (OWNER) sikeresen módosít - 200 OK
PUT http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{davidToken}}

{
  "name": "Csapatprojekt - frissítve",
  "description": "OWNER simán átírhatja"
}

### Tagok listázása mindkét token-nel - mindkettő 200 OK
GET http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{davidToken}}

###
GET http://localhost:8080/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{annaToken}}